{"tid":2139281,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"刀劍神域班美國佬冇黑人,係咪白人祟拜主義","createTime":"2020-08-04T07:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T13:31:02.000Z","uid":8307,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b7d46c9dd998bc298c4d176ad9d8946ec48b1dc6","tid":2139281,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:40:43.000Z","msg":"成套刀劍神域入面得主角群有個拎斧頭光頭黑人<br />\n嚴重地將黑人既外觀定型,令人覺得黑人只係有力量冇咩腦,同埋冇頭髮<br />\n但係初初睇話哂刀劍神域都係日本遊戲,少外國人都好正常<br />\n早期唯一一個有戲份既外國人係黑人,原本都覺得個作者係尊重黑人人權<br />\n點知依家最新講美國入侵小日本,成隊美國人部隊都係冇黑人,仲要講日文<br />\n我懷疑比人操控個班紅衛兵除低左個頭盔都係黑人黎,想影射黑人智商低"},{"pid":"c6a9d3ed8094d61e2126f66881822e503658c11d","tid":2139281,"uid":105678,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:44:52.000Z","msg":"擺明啦，桐人第三季頭都話想去美國讀書，明明有得讀清華南洋呢啲，係都要過美洲，根本暗撐美帝朝貢體系，仲要白人為主嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b201ea3f4e1d2f544c468343ca0a7f59727f82fe","tid":2139281,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:48:06.000Z","msg":"黎蛇好波"},{"pid":"979e94ec48ca4188152bd1da99401ebacddf5f7b","tid":2139281,"uid":299548,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:53:37.000Z","msg":"桐人=黑色劍士<br />\n暗示黑人嘅強大"},{"pid":"ee0f685aac0a06a61a71f5a8a9bdeafbd1bc20f8","tid":2139281,"uid":48149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:59:25.000Z","msg":"有艾基爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a1bae88dd57b84797345dab879249b0a9c3375","tid":2139281,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee0f685aac0a06a61a71f5a8a9bdeafbd1bc20f8","tid":2139281,"uid":48149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:59:25.000Z","msg":"有艾基爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:08:30.000Z","msg":"艾基爾咪個光頭斧頭佬"},{"pid":"65f8479ebfa1e8fe81289ea616d42737f454cb89","tid":2139281,"uid":2223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,